<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Check box <Bold>"EnableAutoScrolling"</Bold> enables or disables the auto scrolling.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Text box <Bold>"AutoScrolling Delta"</Bold> helps to set the delta of auto scrolling.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Button <Bold>"Start Monitoring"</Bold> helps to start adding data to chart series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Button <Bold>"Stop Monitoring"</Bold> helps to stop adding data to chart series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Combo box <Bold>"Palette"</Bold> helps to select the palette for chart series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>
